snippet.title: Hello Girl (Visual Novel Trailer)
snippet.description:
Have you ever felt like a rabbit with a telephone? Hello Girl is a thrilling kinetic visual novel about connection and disconnection, set during a time of great uncertainty. 

Download for free for PC, Mac, and Linux
https://imoteam.itch.io/hello-girl

Special edition coming soon to Steam, wishlist it today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3330860/Hello_Girl/

IMO Team is:
Merilynn F. Paisley
Mentha Nolana
Mara Welsley
and Naja D'egoutter

Follow IMO Team on Bluesky:
https://bsky.app/profile/maillard.love

Support IMO Team on Ko-fi:
https://ko-fi.com/imo_team
